khlone = a local/remote coordinator that enables remote robot clones

key concepts:
- one cloud machine per worksite (typically per git worktree)
- local tui handles dispatch, status, attach, conflict resolution
- sync via git patches (batch), not live filesystem mount
- reconnect on dropped connections, queue when offline
- conflict notification + manual resolution (no auto-merge)
- async batch model, not teletype/real-time

